RJR Nabisco Inc issue 100 mln dlr eurobond due June 30 1994 pay 8-3/4 pct price 101-3/8 pct lead manager Bank America International Ltd said. This confirms earlier report bond market sources. The issue investor option par non-callable. The sell concession 1-1/8 pct management underwriting combine pay 1/2 pct. The issue available denomination 1000 10000 dlrs listing Luxembourg. The payment date June 30. REUTER 